<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-occupied-with">be occupied with</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>忙着做……；忙于某事物</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have been so occupied with work that I haven’t had time for social activities.
工作太忙，我一直没有时间参加社交活动。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 5</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The new comers were occupied (in) writing letters home.
新来的人正忙着给家里写信。</p></div></div>